"title": "8409: decision-making, and providence",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8409",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>People need guidance from God about how they should make up their minds on difficult issues. God gives them this through the Holy Spirit, the Scriptures, individuals, groups and other external means.</p>\n<h2>Decisions should be grounded in a relationship with God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:5-Prov3:6\">PRO 3:5–3:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps23:1-Ps23:3\">PSA 23:1–23:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps25:4-Ps25:5\">PSA 25:4–25:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps25:8-Ps25:9\">PSA 25:8–25:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps25:12\">PSA 25:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov9:10\">PRO 9:10</a> <em>Wisdom involves making right moral decisions</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:31-Matt6:33\">MAT 6:31–6:33</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:29-Luke12:31\">LUK 12:29–12:31</a></p>\n<h2>God guides decision-making</h2>\n<h3>Through Scripture</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:16-2Tim3:17\">2TI 3:16–3:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:7-Ps19:11\">PSA 19:7–19:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:9\">PSA 119:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:11\">PSA 119:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:98-Ps119:100\">PSA 119:98–119:100</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:104-Ps119:105\">PSA 119:104–119:105</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:130\">PSA 119:130</a>MAT <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps4:4\">4:4</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:4\">LUK 4:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:3\">DEU 8:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:7\">MAT 4:7</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:12\">LUK 4:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:16\">DEU 6:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:10\">MAT 4:10</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:8\">LUK 4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:13\">DEU 6:13</a></p>\n<h3>Through supernatural intervention</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:9\">ACT 18:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen28:10-Gen28:15\">GEN 28:10–28:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam16:6-1Sam16:7\">1SA 16:6–16:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam16:12\">1SA 16:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:19-Isa30:21\">ISA 30:19–30:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:6-Jer32:9\">JER 32:6–32:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:10-Acts9:16\">ACT 9:10–9:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:9-Acts10:16\">ACT 10:9–10:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:27-Acts11:30\">ACT 11:27–11:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:10-Acts21:11\">ACT 21:10–21:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:19\">ACT 26:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:29-1Cor14:30\">1CO 14:29–14:30</a></p>\n<h3>Through prayer</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:5-Jas1:6\">JAS 1:5–1:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:9-1Kgs3:12\">1KI 3:9–3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov2:3-Prov2:6\">PRO 2:3–2:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:7-Matt7:11\">MAT 7:7–7:11</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:9-Luke11:13\">LUK 11:9–11:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:22\">MAT 21:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:18\">EPH 6:18</a></p>\n<h3>Through circumstances</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:1-Acts6:4\">ACT 6:1–6:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num13:1-Num13:3\">NUM 13:1–13:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:28-Deut32:29\">DEU 32:28–32:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh2:23-Josh2:24\">JOS 2:23–2:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth2:2-Ruth2:3\">RUT 2:2–2:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:26-1Kgs3:28\">1KI 3:26–3:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:19-Acts15:22\">ACT 15:19–15:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:3\">ACT 16:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:3\">ACT 20:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:16\">ACT 20:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:8-1Cor16:9\">1CO 16:8–16:9</a></p>\n<h2>The work of the Holy Spirit in decision-making</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:16-John14:17\">JHN 14:16–14:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:26\">JHN 14:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:13-John16:15\">JHN 16:13–16:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:29\">ACT 8:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:19\">ACT 10:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:2\">ACT 13:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:28\">ACT 15:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:6-Acts16:10\">ACT 16:6–16:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:20\">1JN 2:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:27\">1JN 2:27</a></p>\n<h2>Motivation in decision-making</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:33\">MAT 6:33</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:17\">COL 3:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps139:23-Ps139:24\">PSA 139:23–139:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:25-Matt20:28\">MAT 20:25–20:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:23\">MAT 23:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:1\">ROM 12:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:31\">1CO 10:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:9\">2CO 5:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:8-Phil4:9\">PHP 4:8–4:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:1\">1TH 4:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:8\">1TH 5:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:12\">1PE 2:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:11\">1PE 4:11</a></p>\n<h2>Humility is essential for divine guidance</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps25:9\">PSA 25:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:12-Deut10:13\">DEU 10:12–10:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps25:14\">PSA 25:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:9-Ps34:10\">PSA 34:9–34:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:1\">PSA 73:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps84:11\">PSA 84:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa58:9-Isa58:11\">ISA 58:9–58:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:20-Dan9:23\">DAN 9:20–9:23</a></p>\n<h2>The need to test guidance</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:19-1Thess5:22\">1TH 5:19–5:22</a></strong></p>",
